rows.label: qst400103_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Maxim!
I'd like to transfer some money.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0002
rows.name:
Why, if it isn't Rex. Pretty rare for a
client to drop cash off in person.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a big sum this time, so Meroro
said I should bring it straight to you.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0004
rows.name:
You're quite the guy, you know.
Not many people send all this money
back to their folks every single month.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0005
rows.name: Haha... It's not that big a deal.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0006
rows.name: So, how much are we talking?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] I don't want to completely empty
my pockets... So after leaving a bit
for myself, let's say...

rows.label: qst400103_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Can you deliver 90,000G to
Correl of Iyasaki Village, please?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0009
rows.name:
Whew, that's quite the healthy sum.
Did you haul up some huge treasure?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0010
rows.name:
Something like that.
I took on a big job from the Chairman.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0011
rows.name:
Now that sure sounds like a pie
I'd like a piece of.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0012
rows.name:
Oh yeah, I got a delivery for you too.
Good thing you dropped by, else I'd've
had to track you down!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0013
rows.name:
It's from that same Auntie Correl
of yours, actually.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0014
rows.name: Ohhh, it's Braised Cloud Sea Shark!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0015
rows.name:
Mmmm, it looks delicious...
I'll have to dig in to that later.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0016
rows.name:
Thanks, Maxim.
Take care of that transfer for me, okay?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0017
rows.name: You can count on me!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0018
rows.name: How much shall I send?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0019
rows.name: Send 90,000G

rows.label: qst400103_msg0020
rows.name: Don't send anything yet.
